name: Gabriel
skill: Deals 4140/4940 DMG to the enemy with the highest ATK, with a 100% chance of inflicting Silence.
ability: Moderate chance to inflict Petrifaction on the enemy with the highest ATK at the start of each wave.
Normal attacks by Divina team members have a moderate chance of inflicting burn.

additional_data.description: The spirit of an archangel responsible for the spreading the word of God. She also serves as liaison to the other archangels. Lately she's been working with an inventor spirit to see if she can find a way to make cellphones function on spirit essence. She's been having a tough time trying to find two free-wheeling angels: one is fixated on young girls, the other is a party angel who tends to wander off and get lost. Behind closed doors she's often found wondering aloud why can't she get more help on the job.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ Trade at Exchange for 75 Mochi 30/11/16 - 31/01/17
◦ The cost increases by 25 Mochi after each exchange
(75, 100, 125, 150, 175)
